citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:45am-11:15am
on 18-JAN-23. The inspector knocked on the door, left a voicemail message, and waited 30 minutes before departing the
facility.
End Section
